As a passionate and results-driven software developer, I specialize in designing, building, and optimizing applications that solve real-world problems. With experience in a variety of programming languages and frameworks, I thrive in collaborative environments, working with cross-functional teams to create innovative software solutions.

I have a strong foundation in Python, Java, Kotlin, JavaScript, Typescript, React, Node.js, etc., and I’m always excited to learn new tools and approaches to stay at the forefront of the ever-evolving tech landscape.
